For the past 46 days I have helped carry the torch across the U.S. for the #SpecialOlympics #unifiedrelay. I have met incredible people and heard truly life changing stories. I was fortunate to share these day to day experiences with my husband as we took on this journey. I encourage anyone to spend some time with the athletes in their communities and get involved. They are some of the best people I have met and the Special Olympics has changed their life for the better. The Bentleys are going to miss our road family and these daily adventures. Everyday we met new people who shared their amazing stories with us. Thank you. #LA2015 #URAA #PassTheFlame
